                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d346">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">845.5018/59: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Officer in Charge at New Delhi</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Merrell</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New Delhi</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-10-11T19:00:00+06:30"
                            >October 11, 1943—7 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received October 11—3:46 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>743. Reference Department’s 538, October 9, 8 p.m. Release of statement deferred
                    pending Department’s reply to Mission’s 727 October 8 unless Department
                    instructs otherwise. External Affairs informs Mission their request made at
                    instance His Majesty’s Government after Food Department had requested His
                    Majesty’s Government to approach Government United States.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Merrell</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
